snippet.title: Nightmare Before Disney (2016) - Nights 1-7 Playthrough
snippet.description:
Happy 8th anniversary FNaTI!

Also, this game is EXTREMELY quiet, so I had to crank up the volume all the way on the video for the sounds to be clearly heard.
